					<div class="single-article-header">
						<div class="card__bugline-container">
			<span class="bugline">PLAGUE AFTER PLAGUE</span>
		</div>						<h1 class="page-title">Locusts and coronavirus: A Biblical nightmare strikes the horn of Africa</h1>
						<div class="article-meta">
							<div class="article-meta__byline_and_date">
	<span class="article-meta__byline">By <a href="https://grist.org/author/emily-pontecorvo/" title="Posts by Emily Pontecorvo" class="author url fn" rel="author">Emily Pontecorvo</a></span>
	<span class="article-meta__date">on Apr 13, 2020</span>
</div>
